// SpreadsheetEditor
// Full-featured spreadsheet editor with sorting, cell editing, row/column CRUD,
// multi-select, clipboard copy/paste (TSV), and column aggregates.

Spreadsheet content is stored as JSON: {columns, rows, aggregates}.
Changes are committed to the store immediately and debounced to the API (500ms).
Clipboard copy produces TSV with a header row. Paste detects if the first row
matches the headers and skips it if so.

FUNCTION SpreadsheetEditor(spreadsheet, ...) -> JSX                    EXPORT
  Parses spreadsheet.content on load.
  Attaches copy/paste event listeners to the container element.
  Renders: column headers (sortable, context-menu on right-click),
  data rows (with row number cell for selection, editable cells),
  aggregates row, and Add Row button.
  Row context menu (right-click on row number): delete/duplicate/insert above.
  Column context menu (right-click on header): delete/duplicate/add column.

---

FUNCTION saveData(newData) -> void
  Updates store immediately via spreadsheet store action.
  Debounces API save by 500ms via setTimeout (cancels previous pending save).

---

FUNCTION handleSort(columnId, direction?) -> void
  Cycles column sort state: asc -> desc -> null (if same column).
  OR sets direction directly if provided.

---

FUNCTION handleCellClick(rowIndex, columnId, value, columnType) -> void
  IF boolean column: toggles the value directly and saves.
  ELSE: opens inline editor for the cell (sets editingCell state).

---

FUNCTION handleCellSave(rowIndex, columnId, rawValue, columnType) -> void
  Parses rawValue by columnType (number, date, boolean, text).
  Saves data, closes inline editor.

---

FUNCTION handleAddRow() -> void
  Appends a new empty row to the data.

---

FUNCTION handleDeleteRow(rowIndex) -> void
  Removes the row at rowIndex.

---

FUNCTION handleDuplicateRow(rowIndex) -> void
  Inserts a copy of the row immediately after rowIndex.

---

FUNCTION handleInsertRowAbove(rowIndex) -> void
  Inserts an empty row before rowIndex.

---

FUNCTION handleDeleteColumn(columnId) -> void
  Removes the column definition and all cell values for that column.

---

FUNCTION handleDuplicateColumn(columnId) -> void
  Inserts a copy of the column definition immediately after the original.

---

FUNCTION handleAddColumn() -> void
  Appends a new empty text column.

---

FUNCTION handleRowSelect(rowIndex, shiftKey) -> void
  Shift+click selects a range from lastSelectedRowRef to rowIndex.
  Click alone toggles the single row.

---

FUNCTION handleContextMenu(e, type, index) -> void
  Prevents default. Sets contextMenu state with position and target row/column.

---

FUNCTION handleTableBodyClick(e) -> void
  Deselects rows when clicking on a non-row-number cell.

---

FUNCTION computeAggregate(column, rows) -> string | number
  Calculates SUM/AVG/COUNT/MIN/MAX based on column.aggregateType.
  Returns the formatted result or an empty string if no aggregate is configured.
